column5: It took less than 2 weeks for my wife and I to get our passports.Lac Seul here we come!!!
Congrats! When all the plans start to come together, it's a great feeling! When do hit the Lac? For our group we leave in ten days, drop the first jig in eleven!! Have a great trip!

I just found my passport in my camera bag the other day. Whoops! That was supposed to go back into the safe when I got back last fall so I don't lose it. That would have been bad as I don't typically grab the passport til right before we leave. Would not have been good if I opened the safe and it wasn't there. Panic would have definitely set in.

WallyDave We'll be at Goose Bay from July 28th through August 10th.It's our Honeymoon.Broke the new boat in on Lake Oahe last night,got worm dirt in the carpet,put limits of walleyes in the livewell,spilled soda also. I'm waiting for your Lac seul report.Bill
